73
00:06:44,435 --> 00:06:46,516
If your eyes hurt, I can be your eyes.

74
00:06:46,836 --> 00:06:48,315
If your leg hurts, I can be your crutch.

75
00:06:50,235 --> 00:06:51,435
All I want is to be with you together.

76
