130
00:12:21,636 --> 00:12:22,435
Let's go back together.

131
00:12:22,835 --> 00:12:23,996
They won't fight with me around.

132
00:12:25,156 --> 00:12:26,236
I miss your mom's cooking.

133
00:12:27,036 --> 00:12:27,516
